Dialogue: 1,0:00:11.95,0:00:14.20,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,是谁住在深海的大菠萝里
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.95,0:00:14.20,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Who lives in a pineapple under the sea?
