Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.20,0:00:19.99,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,SpongeBob SquarePants
Dialogue: 1,0:00:19.99,0:00:22.25,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,如果四处探险是你的愿望
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.99,0:00:22.25,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,If nautical nonsense be something you wish
Dialogue: 1,0:00:22.25,0:00:23.96,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,海绵宝宝
