Dialogue: 1,0:00:58.99,0:01:01.49,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,裤头村里  正是星期天的早晨
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.99,0:01:01.49,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,It is Sunday morning in Bikini Bottom
Dialogue: 1,0:01:01.49,0:01:05.25,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,章鱼哥练竖笛的时间就要到了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.49,0:01:02.66,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,and it is about time
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.66,0:01:05.25,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,for Squidward to practice his clarinet
Dialogue: 1,0:01:05.25,0:01:07.13,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,所以快把你的耳塞准备好吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.25,0:01:07.13,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,So get your ear plugs ready
Dialogue: 1,0:01:09.34,0:01:13.09,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我该给裤头村来点真正的音乐了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.34,0:01:13.09,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I think I'll treat Bikini Bottom to some real music
Dialogue: 1,0:01:28.27,0:01:30.61,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,早上好  章鱼哥
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.27,0:01:30.61,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Good morning, Squidward
Dialogue: 1,0:01:30.61,0:01:32.23,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,要去捉水母吗
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.61,0:01:32.23,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Wanna go jellyfishing?
Dialogue: 1,0:01:35.15,0:01:36.32,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,太棒了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.15,0:01:36.32,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Great
Dialogue: 1,0:01:36.32,0:01:37.36,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我们马上就到
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.32,0:01:37.36,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,We'll be right over
Dialogue: 1,0:01:42.04,0:01:43.70,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我还在想是谁呢
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.04,0:01:43.70,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I wonder who that could be
Dialogue: 1,0:01:45.58,0:01:46.96,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,准备好出发了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.58,0:01:46.96,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Ready to go?
Dialogue: 1,0:01:46.96,0:01:49.13,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不对  我没准备好
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.96,0:01:49.13,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,No, I'm not ready to go
Dialogue: 1,0:01:49.96,0:01:51.92,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,他不想跟我们玩
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.96,0:01:51.92,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,He doesn't wanna play with us
Dialogue: 1,0:01:51.92,0:01:52.80,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,才不呢  派大星
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.92,0:01:52.80,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,No, Patrick
Dialogue: 1,0:01:52.80,0:01:53.92,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,只是没准备好而已
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.80,0:01:53.92,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,he's just not ready
