Dialogue: 1,0:02:32.54,0:02:33.25,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,哎哟喂
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.54,0:02:33.25,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Sheesh
Dialogue: 1,0:02:33.25,0:02:35.55,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你今天不是该去上班的吗  海绵宝宝
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.25,0:02:35.55,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Shouldn't you be at work today, SpongeBob?
Dialogue: 1,0:02:35.55,0:02:37.22,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我是想今天上班的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.55,0:02:37.22,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'd love to be at work today
Dialogue: 1,0:02:37.76,0:02:39.01,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,可今天星期天
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.76,0:02:39.01,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,But it's Sunday
Dialogue: 1,0:02:39.01,0:02:40.64,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,蟹堡王关门
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.01,0:02:40.64,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,The Krusty Krab is closed
Dialogue: 1,0:02:42.18,0:02:43.55,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,等会啊
