Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.84,0:03:19.01,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Well, he's not here
Dialogue: 1,0:03:19.01,0:03:22.34,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我敢赌他等不及先到水母田去了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.01,0:03:20.47,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'll bet that eager-beaver's
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.47,0:03:22.34,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,already down at Jellyfish Fields
Dialogue: 1,0:03:23.93,0:03:25.26,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,他们终于走了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.93,0:03:25.26,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,They're finally gone
