Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.31,0:03:28.02,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What the...?
Dialogue: 1,0:03:28.02,0:03:28.64,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,锁上了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.02,0:03:28.64,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Locked?
