Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.35,0:03:34.44,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Someone will realize I'm gone and come looking for me
Dialogue: 1,0:03:34.44,0:03:37.44,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我就马上可以出去了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.44,0:03:37.44,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'll be out of here in no time
