Dialogue: 1,0:03:56.88,0:03:58.80,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,有只被冻住的头足类动物
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.88,0:03:58.80,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,A frozen cephalopod
Dialogue: 1,0:04:08.77,0:04:10.81,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我就马上可以出去了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.77,0:04:10.81,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'll be out of here in no time
Dialogue: 1,0:04:10.81,0:04:11.98,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你好  原始生物
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.81,0:04:11.98,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Greetings, primitive
Dialogue: 1,0:04:12.19,0:04:12.52,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,海
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.19,0:04:12.52,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Sp...
Dialogue: 1,0:04:12.85,0:04:14.06,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,海绵宝宝
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.85,0:04:14.06,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,SpongeBob?
Dialogue: 1,0:04:14.06,0:04:15.40,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,是你吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.06,0:04:15.40,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Is that you?
Dialogue: 1,0:04:15.73,0:04:16.73,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,海绵宝宝
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.73,0:04:16.73,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,SpongeBob?
Dialogue: 1,0:04:17.06,0:04:17.98,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.06,0:04:17.98,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,No
Dialogue: 1,0:04:17.98,0:04:19.57,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我是机器宝宝
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.98,0:04:19.57,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I am SpongeTron
Dialogue: 1,0:04:19.90,0:04:21.03,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,欢迎来到未来
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.90,0:04:21.03,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Welcome to the future
Dialogue: 1,0:04:21.99,0:04:22.40,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,说什么
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.99,0:04:22.40,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 1,0:04:22.61,0:04:23.99,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,欢迎来到未来
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.61,0:04:23.99,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Welcome to the future
Dialogue: 1,0:04:25.45,0:04:27.03,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,未来
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.45,0:04:27.03,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,The future
Dialogue: 1,0:04:30.41,0:04:30.79,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,好  好吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.41,0:04:30.79,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,O-okay
Dialogue: 1,0:04:31.20,0:04:32.16,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这是怎么了这
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.20,0:04:32.16,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What's going on here?
Dialogue: 1,0:04:32.62,0:04:33.66,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,怎么所有东西都是
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.62,0:04:33.66,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Why is everything
Dialogue: 1,0:04:33.96,0:04:34.50,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,镀了铬的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.96,0:04:34.50,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,chrome?
Dialogue: 1,0:04:34.67,0:04:37.17,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,未来所有东西都镀上了金属铬
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.67,0:04:37.17,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Everything is chrome in the future
Dialogue: 1,0:04:37.17,0:04:37.46,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,什
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.17,0:04:37.46,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Wha...?
Dialogue: 1,0:04:40.34,0:04:42.72,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,老天爷啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.34,0:04:42.72,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Oh, my...
Dialogue: 1,0:04:43.22,0:04:44.01,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,根本不可能
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.22,0:04:44.01,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Impossible
Dialogue: 1,0:04:44.76,0:04:46.09,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,他在说谎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.76,0:04:46.09,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,He's lying
Dialogue: 1,0:04:55.39,0:04:57.23,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,他还真没说错
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.39,0:04:57.23,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,He's right
Dialogue: 1,0:04:57.23,0:04:58.86,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我当然是对的  章鱼哥
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.23,0:04:58.86,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Of course I'm right, Squidward
Dialogue: 1,0:04:59.19,0:05:00.57,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,问问我的复制体
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.19,0:05:00.57,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Just ask my clones
Dialogue: 1,0:05:00.57,0:05:02.24,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,机器宝宝XYZ吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.57,0:05:02.24,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,SpongeTrons X, Y, and Z
Dialogue: 1,0:05:02.40,0:05:06.16,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,其他的字母也在这是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.40,0:05:06.16,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Are the other letters of the alphabet involved here?
Dialogue: 1,0:05:06.16,0:05:06.99,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,当然了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.16,0:05:06.99,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Sure
Dialogue: 1,0:05:06.99,0:05:08.57,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,总共有486个
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.99,0:05:08.57,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,All 486 of them
Dialogue: 1,0:05:15.67,0:05:18.21,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,未来
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.67,0:05:18.21,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Future
Dialogue: 1,0:05:18.67,0:05:21.25,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,未来
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.67,0:05:21.25,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Future
Dialogue: 1,0:05:21.75,0:05:24.47,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,未来
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.75,0:05:24.47,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Future
Dialogue: 1,0:05:25.34,0:05:27.13,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,未来
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.34,0:05:27.13,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Future
Dialogue: 1,0:05:28.01,0:05:28.55,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,谢谢了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.01,0:05:28.55,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Thanks
Dialogue: 1,0:05:29.35,0:05:30.18,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,给我听好
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.35,0:05:30.18,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Now listen
Dialogue: 1,0:05:30.56,0:05:31.43,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,都听清楚
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.56,0:05:31.43,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,All of you
Dialogue: 1,0:05:31.43,0:05:33.18,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我不属于这里
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.43,0:05:33.18,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I don't belong here
Dialogue: 1,0:05:33.18,0:05:35.35,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这就是一可怕的错误
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.18,0:05:35.35,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,This is all a horrible mistake
Dialogue: 1,0:05:35.35,0:05:36.14,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,求你们了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.35,0:05:36.14,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Please
Dialogue: 1,0:05:36.14,0:05:37.52,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,好歹也想想办法吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.14,0:05:37.52,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,We've got to do something
Dialogue: 1,0:05:38.52,0:05:39.69,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,捉水母
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.52,0:05:39.69,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Jellyfishing
Dialogue: 1,0:05:41.82,0:05:43.99,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,是不是有人说了  捉水母
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.82,0:05:43.99,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Did somebody say, "jellyfishing"?
Dialogue: 1,0:05:43.99,0:05:45.32,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,嗨  派大双
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.99,0:05:45.32,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Hi, PatTron
Dialogue: 1,0:05:46.32,0:05:47.28,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,听我说好了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.32,0:05:47.28,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Just listen to me
Dialogue: 1,0:05:47.66,0:05:49.53,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我不应该在这里的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.66,0:05:49.53,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'm not supposed to be here
Dialogue: 1,0:05:49.53,0:05:52.70,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我得回到我自己的时空去
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.53,0:05:52.70,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I've gotta get home to my own time period
Dialogue: 1,0:05:52.70,0:05:53.87,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我必须要走
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.70,0:05:53.87,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I've gotta go
Dialogue: 1,0:05:54.08,0:05:55.83,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,那你怎么不早说
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.08,0:05:55.83,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Well, why didn't you just ask?
Dialogue: 1,0:05:55.83,0:05:58.12,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,时间机器就在走廊尽头左手边
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.83,0:05:58.12,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,The time machine is down the hall, to the left
Dialogue: 1,0:06:08.30,0:06:09.43,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,啊对
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.30,0:06:09.43,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Oh, yeah
Dialogue: 1,0:06:09.43,0:06:10.97,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,那个是开罐器
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.43,0:06:10.97,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,That one's the can opener
Dialogue: 1,0:06:10.97,0:06:12.22,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,走右边的试试看
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.97,0:06:12.22,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,But try the one on the right
Dialogue: 1,0:06:17.48,0:06:19.77,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,要是让我来装修  才不选这种丑内饰
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.48,0:06:19.77,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Well, I wouldn't have chosen this interior
Dialogue: 1,0:06:20.77,0:06:21.31,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这什么
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.77,0:06:21.31,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What's this?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.31,0:06:28.20,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(977.787,171.333)}未来
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.31,0:06:28.20,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(951.108,915.333)}过去
Dialogue: 1,0:06:21.65,0:06:24.65,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,既然未来有海绵宝宝
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.65,0:06:24.65,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Well, if SpongeBob exists in the future
Dialogue: 1,0:06:24.65,0:06:26.61,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我最好要去
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.65,0:06:26.61,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'd better go to
Dialogue: 1,0:06:26.61,0:06:28.20,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,过去
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.61,0:06:28.20,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,the past
Dialogue: 1,0:06:48.80,0:06:49.55,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,好原始
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.80,0:06:49.55,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Primitive
Dialogue: 1,0:06:50.97,0:06:52.89,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,有点远古世界的魅力
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.97,0:06:52.89,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Has sort of an old-world charm
Dialogue: 1,0:06:55.06,0:06:57.81,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我看这时候怕是还没有发明礼貌
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.06,0:06:57.81,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I guess this is before manners were invented
Dialogue: 1,0:06:58.60,0:07:01.15,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,至少没有海绵小鬼的影子
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.60,0:07:01.15,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Well, at least there's no sign of SpongeBrat
Dialogue: 1,0:07:01.15,0:07:04.69,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,现在总算可以跟我竖笛孤独在一起了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.15,0:07:04.69,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Maybe now I can finally be alone with my clarinet
Dialogue: 1,0:07:18.96,0:07:19.33,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.96,0:07:19.33,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 1,0:07:29.13,0:07:30.05,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,海绵宝宝
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.13,0:07:30.05,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,SpongeBob?
Dialogue: 1,0:07:32.93,0:07:33.72,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,别过来
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.93,0:07:33.72,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Stay back
Dialogue: 1,0:07:39.27,0:07:39.85,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不用了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.27,0:07:39.85,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,No thanks
Dialogue: 1,0:07:51.86,0:07:52.53,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你好啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.86,0:07:52.53,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Hi there
Dialogue: 1,0:07:53.11,0:07:54.32,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,那个  我最好马上走开
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.11,0:07:54.32,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Well, I better be going now
Dialogue: 1,0:07:55.66,0:07:57.28,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,对  这是我胳膊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.66,0:07:57.28,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Yes, that's my arm
Dialogue: 1,0:08:03.08,0:08:03.79,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,真是亲热
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.08,0:08:03.79,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,That's sweet
Dialogue: 1,0:08:07.29,0:08:09.42,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,干嘛  你现在要洗澡除跳蚤了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.29,0:08:09.42,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What, is it time for your flea bath now?
Dialogue: 1,0:08:10.51,0:08:12.38,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,看啊  就一小水母而已
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.51,0:08:12.38,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Look, it's just a little jellyfish
Dialogue: 1,0:08:22.02,0:08:23.60,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,好吧  我要走开了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.02,0:08:23.60,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Well, I'm going away now
Dialogue: 1,0:08:26.11,0:08:28.11,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这有个荫凉的风水宝地
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.11,0:08:28.11,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Here's a nice, shady spot
Dialogue: 1,0:08:28.11,0:08:30.07,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,还离那些傻子远远的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.11,0:08:30.07,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,away from those fools
Dialogue: 1,0:08:48.92,0:08:51.13,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你们这些白痴在搞什么
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.92,0:08:51.13,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What are you simpletons doing?
Dialogue: 1,0:08:51.13,0:08:53.22,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你们应该要捉住这玩意的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.13,0:08:53.22,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You're supposed to catch these things
Dialogue: 1,0:08:53.22,0:08:54.84,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,而不是拿这玩意来自虐
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.22,0:08:54.84,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,not torture yourself with them
Dialogue: 1,0:08:56.64,0:08:58.01,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,遮羞布拿来
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.64,0:08:58.01,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Give me those loincloths
Dialogue: 1,0:09:02.10,0:09:03.10,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,真不敢相信
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.10,0:09:03.10,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I can't believe it
Dialogue: 1,0:09:04.69,0:09:06.94,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这样差不多就能万事顺利了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.69,0:09:06.94,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,This oughta make things go a little smoother
Dialogue: 1,0:09:12.36,0:09:13.40,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,把那些给我
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.36,0:09:13.40,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Give me those things
Dialogue: 1,0:09:13.40,0:09:15.91,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你们应该要这样子捉住那玩意
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.40,0:09:15.91,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You're supposed to catch them, like this
Dialogue: 1,0:09:17.91,0:09:20.16,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这个叫做捉水母
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.91,0:09:20.16,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,It's called jellyfishing
Dialogue: 1,0:09:30.04,0:09:31.30,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,终于啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.04,0:09:31.30,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Finally
Dialogue: 1,0:09:53.23,0:09:54.90,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,让我离开这
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.23,0:09:54.90,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Get me outta here
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.95,0:09:57.61,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(628.291,707.333)}未来
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.91,0:10:00.70,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(767.022,704.667)}空
Dialogue: 1,0:10:00.16,0:10:00.70,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,废物
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.16,0:10:00.70,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Loser
Dialogue: 1,0:10:36.90,0:10:37.82,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,他不在这
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.90,0:10:37.82,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,He's not here
Dialogue: 1,0:10:38.45,0:10:40.11,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,没有海绵宝宝了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.45,0:10:40.11,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,No more SpongeBob
Dialogue: 1,0:10:40.45,0:10:41.24,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,没有了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.45,0:10:41.24,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,No more
Dialogue: 1,0:10:41.74,0:10:46.54,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我终于有地方可以一个人
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.74,0:10:46.54,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I may finally have found a place where I can be all
Dialogue: 1,0:10:48.62,0:10:50.50,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,孤独
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.62,0:10:50.50,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,alone
Dialogue: 1,0:10:50.50,0:10:58.42,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,孤独
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.50,0:10:58.42,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Alone
Dialogue: 1,0:10:59.43,0:11:00.89,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,孤独
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.43,0:11:00.89,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Alone
Dialogue: 1,0:11:01.43,0:11:03.05,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,孤独
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.43,0:11:03.05,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Alone
Dialogue: 1,0:11:03.05,0:11:04.35,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,孤独
