Dialogue: 1,0:16:09.99,0:16:10.99,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.99,0:16:10.99,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Oh yeah
Dialogue: 1,0:16:11.49,0:16:12.15,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,逮到你了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.49,0:16:12.15,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Gotcha
Dialogue: 1,0:16:12.15,0:16:12.78,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,海绵宝宝
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.15,0:16:12.78,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,SpongeBob
Dialogue: 1,0:16:12.78,0:16:13.07,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.78,0:16:13.07,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 1,0:16:14.78,0:16:16.41,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我要假装无事发生
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.78,0:16:16.41,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'm going to pretend that didn't happen
Dialogue: 1,0:16:16.41,0:16:18.83,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,要么做饭要么走人  海绵宝宝
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.41,0:16:18.83,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Now fill these orders or leave, SpongeBob
Dialogue: 1,0:16:18.83,0:16:20.29,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,今天生意忙的很
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.83,0:16:20.29,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,We're very busy today
Dialogue: 1,0:16:22.62,0:16:23.92,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,上菜了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.62,0:16:23.92,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Order up
Dialogue: 1,0:16:31.59,0:16:32.38,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,海绵宝宝
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.59,0:16:32.38,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,SpongeBob
Dialogue: 1,0:16:32.38,0:16:33.26,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你是要
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.38,0:16:33.26,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Now are you gonna
Dialogue: 1,0:16:33.63,0:16:34.47,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,章鱼哥
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.63,0:16:34.47,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Squidward
Dialogue: 1,0:16:34.47,0:16:36.68,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我刚在办公室查账  然后呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.47,0:16:36.68,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I was going through some records back in me office and
Dialogue: 1,0:16:37.51,0:16:39.85,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你可终于有假发了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.51,0:16:39.85,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,So, you got the hairpiece after all
Dialogue: 1,0:16:40.77,0:16:41.81,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我的腿
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.77,0:16:41.81,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,My leg
Dialogue: 1,0:16:41.81,0:16:44.31,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,以为你可以在我上班时偷袭我是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.81,0:16:44.31,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Thought you could sneak up on me at work, did ya?
Dialogue: 1,0:16:44.31,0:16:45.44,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,想得美
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.31,0:16:45.44,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Well, you can't
Dialogue: 1,0:16:45.44,0:16:46.65,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,因为我敏捷
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.44,0:16:46.65,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,'Cause I'm fast
Dialogue: 1,0:16:46.65,0:16:47.65,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我狠
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.65,0:16:47.65,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'm mean
Dialogue: 1,0:16:47.65,0:16:49.19,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,还可以这样
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.65,0:16:49.19,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,and I can do this
Dialogue: 1,0:16:54.45,0:16:56.37,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,教训了她一顿可真是好
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.45,0:16:56.37,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Took care of her, yes I did
Dialogue: 1,0:16:56.82,0:16:57.99,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,老板好
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.82,0:16:57.99,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Ahoy, sir
Dialogue: 1,0:16:57.99,0:16:58.78,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,那是怎么回事
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.99,0:16:58.78,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What was that?
Dialogue: 1,0:16:59.28,0:17:00.37,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,可是老板
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.28,0:17:00.37,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,But, sir
Dialogue: 1,0:17:00.37,0:17:01.95,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,她偷袭我
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.37,0:17:01.95,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,She snuck up on me
Dialogue: 1,0:17:02.58,0:17:05.00,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,擅闯了我自己的道场
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.58,0:17:05.00,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,In my own dojo
Dialogue: 1,0:17:05.46,0:17:08.29,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你是不是换新的过敏药吃了  小子
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.46,0:17:08.29,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Are you on some new allergy medication, boy?
Dialogue: 1,0:17:08.29,0:17:09.21,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不是的  老板
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.29,0:17:09.21,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,No, sir
Dialogue: 1,0:17:09.21,0:17:10.88,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,练空手道而已
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.21,0:17:10.88,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Just practicing my karate, sir
Dialogue: 1,0:17:10.88,0:17:12.80,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,也可以说成是空手道
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.88,0:17:12.80,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Or kara-tay, as some call it
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.88,0:17:12.80,注释,,0,0,0,,[ kara-tay：karate的不同读法 ]
Dialogue: 1,0:17:12.80,0:17:14.05,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,空手道
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.80,0:17:14.05,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Kara-tay?
Dialogue: 1,0:17:14.38,0:17:16.76,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你应该要给我练赚钱道的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.38,0:17:16.76,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You should be making me money-ay
Dialogue: 1,0:17:16.76,0:17:18.39,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,用锅铲道来练
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.76,0:17:18.39,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,With your spatu-lae
Dialogue: 1,0:17:18.39,0:17:19.47,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,现在给我回去干活
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.39,0:17:19.47,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Now get back to work
Dialogue: 1,0:17:19.93,0:17:21.52,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,遵命老板
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.93,0:17:21.52,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Aye aye, capi-tay
Dialogue: 1,0:17:22.14,0:17:23.23,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,假发不错章鱼哥
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.14,0:17:23.23,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Nice hairpiece, Squidward
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.10,0:17:26.90,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(374.84,438)}蟹堡王
Dialogue: 1,0:17:26.90,0:17:29.11,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,海绵宝宝  你拖过卫生间地板了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.90,0:17:29.11,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,SpongeBob, did you get those bathrooms mopped yet?
Dialogue: 1,0:17:29.61,0:17:30.44,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,拖过了大姐
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.61,0:17:30.44,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Yes, ma'am
Dialogue: 1,0:17:30.44,0:17:31.11,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我是说大哥
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.44,0:17:31.11,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I mean, sir
Dialogue: 1,0:17:31.11,0:17:32.07,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我是说老板
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.11,0:17:32.07,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I mean, boss
Dialogue: 1,0:17:32.07,0:17:32.99,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我是说全权大臣
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.07,0:17:32.99,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I mean, poobah
Dialogue: 1,0:17:32.99,0:17:33.86,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,去拖
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.99,0:17:33.86,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Go
Dialogue: 1,0:17:49.88,0:17:50.75,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,珊迪
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.88,0:17:50.75,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Sandy
Dialogue: 1,0:17:54.92,0:17:55.55,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不准这样了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.92,0:17:55.55,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,No more
Dialogue: 1,0:17:55.97,0:17:56.97,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,可是蟹老板
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.97,0:17:56.97,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,But, Mr. Krabs
Dialogue: 1,0:17:58.89,0:18:01.22,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不准再搞空手道了  小子
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.89,0:18:01.22,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,No more of this karate stuff, lad
Dialogue: 1,0:18:01.22,0:18:02.47,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,再做就开除你
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.22,0:18:02.47,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Or you're fired
Dialogue: 1,0:18:05.60,0:18:06.39,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,开除
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.60,0:18:06.39,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Fired?
Dialogue: 1,0:18:07.85,0:18:09.44,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不准再搞空手道了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.85,0:18:09.44,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,No more karate?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.94,0:18:09.44,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(374.84,446)}蟹堡王
Dialogue: 1,0:18:09.61,0:18:11.36,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我要怎么跟珊迪解释
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.61,0:18:11.36,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,How am I gonna tell Sandy?
Dialogue: 1,0:18:12.57,0:18:13.36,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,珊迪等等
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.57,0:18:13.36,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Sandy, wait
Dialogue: 1,0:18:13.36,0:18:14.23,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我不可以了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.36,0:18:14.23,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I can't
Dialogue: 1,0:18:14.23,0:18:16.57,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,蟹老板说我不能搞空手道了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.23,0:18:16.57,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Mr. Krabs said I have to give up karate
Dialogue: 1,0:18:17.45,0:18:18.57,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,真的吗  海绵宝宝
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.45,0:18:18.57,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Sure, SpongeBob
Dialogue: 1,0:18:18.57,0:18:19.62,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,别别
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.57,0:18:19.62,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,No, no
Dialogue: 1,0:18:19.62,0:18:20.57,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,真的  珊迪
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.62,0:18:20.57,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Really, Sandy
Dialogue: 1,0:18:20.57,0:18:21.07,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,别弄了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.57,0:18:21.07,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Stop
Dialogue: 1,0:18:22.74,0:18:24.79,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我才不会上当的  海绵宝宝
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.74,0:18:24.79,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'm not falling for it, SpongeBob
Dialogue: 1,0:18:24.79,0:18:26.00,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,别弄了  真的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.79,0:18:26.00,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,No, really
Dialogue: 1,0:18:26.50,0:18:27.37,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,求你别这样了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.50,0:18:27.37,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Please, stop
Dialogue: 1,0:18:28.54,0:18:29.04,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,搞什么
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.54,0:18:29.04,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What the?
Dialogue: 1,0:18:30.42,0:18:31.21,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,海绵宝宝
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.42,0:18:31.21,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,SpongeBob
Dialogue: 1,0:18:32.09,0:18:33.21,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,蟹老板
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.09,0:18:33.21,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Mr. Krabs
Dialogue: 1,0:18:33.21,0:18:36.30,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我刚刚跟你讲什么了  小子
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.21,0:18:36.30,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What did I just get through telling ye, lad?
Dialogue: 1,0:18:36.30,0:18:37.38,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,可是我
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.30,0:18:37.38,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,But I
Dialogue: 1,0:18:37.72,0:18:38.05,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,她
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.72,0:18:38.05,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,She
Dialogue: 1,0:18:38.05,0:18:38.97,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,海绵宝宝
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.05,0:18:38.97,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,SpongeBob
Dialogue: 1,0:18:39.51,0:18:41.35,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你被开除了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.51,0:18:41.35,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You're fired
Dialogue: 1,0:18:43.31,0:18:44.06,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,开除了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.31,0:18:44.06,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Fired?
Dialogue: 1,0:18:47.93,0:18:49.19,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,海绵宝宝
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.93,0:18:49.19,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,SpongeBob?
Dialogue: 1,0:18:57.40,0:18:58.11,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,等等
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.40,0:18:58.11,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Wait
Dialogue: 1,0:18:58.11,0:19:00.24,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,蟹老板  不是他的错
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.11,0:19:00.24,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Mr. Krabs, it's not his fault
Dialogue: 1,0:19:00.24,0:19:00.61,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.24,0:19:00.61,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,It's
Dialogue: 1,0:19:00.61,0:19:01.53,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,是我的错
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.61,0:19:01.53,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,it's mine
Dialogue: 1,0:19:01.53,0:19:02.49,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,他本来要告诉我
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.53,0:19:02.49,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,He tried to tell me
Dialogue: 1,0:19:02.49,0:19:03.16,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,可我
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.49,0:19:03.16,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,but I
Dialogue: 1,0:19:03.16,0:19:04.16,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我没有听
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.16,0:19:04.16,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I wouldn't listen
Dialogue: 1,0:19:12.13,0:19:14.17,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,再给他一次机会吧  求你了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.13,0:19:14.17,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Give him another chance, please?
Dialogue: 1,0:19:17.42,0:19:19.26,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,好了  小子
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.42,0:19:19.26,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,All right, me boy
Dialogue: 1,0:19:19.26,0:19:21.18,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我再给你一次机会
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.26,0:19:21.18,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'll give you a second chance
Dialogue: 1,0:19:21.18,0:19:23.35,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不准再弄空手道了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.18,0:19:23.35,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,But no more karate
Dialogue: 1,0:19:23.35,0:19:25.47,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,那会毒害你的精神
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.35,0:19:25.47,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,It's poisoning your mind
Dialogue: 1,0:19:28.02,0:19:28.98,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这些哺乳动物啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.02,0:19:28.98,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Mammals
Dialogue: 1,0:19:29.85,0:19:31.23,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,真见鬼
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.85,0:19:31.23,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Aww, shoot
Dialogue: 1,0:19:31.23,0:19:32.52,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,海绵宝宝
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.23,0:19:32.52,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,SpongeBob
Dialogue: 1,0:19:32.52,0:19:33.73,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我早该相信你的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.52,0:19:33.73,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I guess you ain't fibbing
Dialogue: 1,0:19:38.19,0:19:40.20,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,反正空手道就要过时了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.19,0:19:40.20,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,That game was getting old anyway
Dialogue: 1,0:19:40.20,0:19:41.61,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,已经不好玩了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.20,0:19:41.61,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,It's not fun anymore
Dialogue: 1,0:19:42.16,0:19:42.86,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我意思是
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.16,0:19:42.86,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I mean
Dialogue: 1,0:19:42.86,0:19:43.87,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这有什么
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.86,0:19:43.87,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,what's so fun about
Dialogue: 1,0:19:44.45,0:19:44.91,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,好玩的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.45,0:19:44.91,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,this?
Dialogue: 1,0:19:49.04,0:19:49.87,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,没
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.04,0:19:49.87,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Nothing
Dialogue: 1,0:19:49.87,0:19:52.17,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,那根本就没什么好玩的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.87,0:19:52.17,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Nothing is fun about that at all
Dialogue: 1,0:19:52.54,0:19:54.29,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我们是可以找到至少有
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.54,0:19:54.29,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,We can find something to do that's at least
Dialogue: 1,0:19:54.67,0:19:56.13,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,九倍好玩的东西的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.67,0:19:56.13,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,nine times as fun
Dialogue: 1,0:19:56.13,0:19:56.71,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,真可以吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.13,0:19:56.71,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,We can?
Dialogue: 1,0:19:57.30,0:19:57.96,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我说的是
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.30,0:19:57.96,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I mean
Dialogue: 1,0:19:57.96,0:19:59.34,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,当然可以了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.96,0:19:59.34,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,sure we can
Dialogue: 1,0:19:59.34,0:20:00.42,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,好啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.34,0:20:00.42,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Yeah
Dialogue: 1,0:20:00.42,0:20:01.43,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,比如说我们可以
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.42,0:20:01.43,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Like we can
Dialogue: 1,0:20:02.93,0:20:04.22,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,可以挤东西
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.93,0:20:04.22,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,We can squeeze things
Dialogue: 1,0:20:09.31,0:20:10.60,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,到底有多好玩呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.31,0:20:10.60,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,How much fun was that?
Dialogue: 1,0:20:10.60,0:20:11.64,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,差不多有点了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.60,0:20:11.64,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Almost some
Dialogue: 1,0:20:13.56,0:20:14.35,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,有了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.56,0:20:14.35,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I know
Dialogue: 1,0:20:14.35,0:20:16.02,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我们可以装成植物
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.35,0:20:16.02,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,We can act like plants
Dialogue: 1,0:20:17.02,0:20:18.53,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,光合作用
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.02,0:20:18.53,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Photosynthesis
Dialogue: 1,0:20:19.03,0:20:20.32,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,光合作用
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.03,0:20:20.32,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Photosynthesis
Dialogue: 1,0:20:21.15,0:20:22.20,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,要去公园吗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.15,0:20:22.20,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Wanna go to the park?
Dialogue: 1,0:20:24.49,0:20:26.62,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,空手道可真是笨
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.49,0:20:26.62,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Karate sure is dumb
Dialogue: 1,0:20:26.62,0:20:28.45,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你说的可真是对
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.62,0:20:28.45,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Yeah, you can say that again
Dialogue: 1,0:20:28.45,0:20:30.50,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我连想到空手道都觉得笨
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.45,0:20:30.50,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I feel dumb just thinking about it
Dialogue: 1,0:20:31.71,0:20:33.62,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我好笨
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.71,0:20:33.62,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'm stupid
Dialogue: 1,0:20:33.62,0:20:35.75,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我爱空手道
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.62,0:20:35.75,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I like karate
Dialogue: 1,0:20:36.84,0:20:38.17,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你爱什么
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.84,0:20:38.17,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You like what?
Dialogue: 1,0:20:38.17,0:20:39.63,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,反正不是空手道
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.17,0:20:39.63,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Not karate
Dialogue: 1,0:20:40.05,0:20:41.84,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我连那玩意是什么都不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.05,0:20:41.84,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I don't even know what that is
Dialogue: 1,0:20:41.84,0:20:42.59,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我也是
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.84,0:20:42.59,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Me, too
Dialogue: 1,0:20:42.59,0:20:43.80,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我什么都不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.59,0:20:43.80,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I don't know what anything is
Dialogue: 1,0:20:43.80,0:20:44.43,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,其实
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.80,0:20:44.43,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,In fact
Dialogue: 1,0:20:50.31,0:20:52.10,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,等会  那听起来好像是
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.31,0:20:52.10,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,For a second, that sounded like
Dialogue: 1,0:20:52.10,0:20:52.73,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,空手道
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.10,0:20:52.73,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Karate?
Dialogue: 1,0:20:52.73,0:20:53.35,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,现在就来吗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.73,0:20:53.35,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Right now?
Dialogue: 1,0:20:53.98,0:20:55.40,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我说的是  才不来
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.98,0:20:55.40,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I mean, no
Dialogue: 1,0:20:55.40,0:20:56.86,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,空手道是个什么玩意
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.40,0:20:56.86,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What is this karate?
Dialogue: 1,0:20:57.73,0:20:59.02,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你三明治上要加什么
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.73,0:20:59.02,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What do you want on your sandwich?
Dialogue: 1,0:20:59.19,0:20:59.90,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,空手道
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.19,0:20:59.90,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Karate
Dialogue: 1,0:20:59.90,0:21:00.86,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你说什么了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.90,0:21:00.86,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What did you say?
Dialogue: 1,0:21:01.23,0:21:02.03,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,芥末酱
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.23,0:21:02.03,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Mustard
Dialogue: 1,0:21:02.03,0:21:02.40,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,芥末酱
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.03,0:21:02.40,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Mustard
Dialogue: 1,0:21:02.40,0:21:04.20,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我三明治上要加芥末酱
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.40,0:21:04.20,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I want mustard on my sandwich
Dialogue: 1,0:21:05.03,0:21:05.70,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,开始吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.03,0:21:05.70,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,There we go
Dialogue: 1,0:21:07.45,0:21:09.49,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你要多少的藤壶块
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.45,0:21:09.49,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,How many slices of barnacle loaf do you want?
Dialogue: 1,0:21:09.49,0:21:09.95,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,一块
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.49,0:21:09.95,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,One
Dialogue: 1,0:21:09.95,0:21:11.37,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,一块就行
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.95,0:21:11.37,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Just one
Dialogue: 1,0:21:11.37,0:21:13.21,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,一块给你
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.37,0:21:13.21,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,One for you
Dialogue: 1,0:21:14.00,0:21:16.17,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,一块给我
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.00,0:21:16.17,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,And one for me
Dialogue: 1,0:21:20.88,0:21:21.71,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,海绵宝宝
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.88,0:21:21.71,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,SpongeBob?
Dialogue: 1,0:21:21.71,0:21:23.34,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,就再来一块吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.71,0:21:23.34,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Maybe just one more
Dialogue: 1,0:21:23.97,0:21:25.22,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我有点饿了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.97,0:21:25.22,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'm kinda hungry
Dialogue: 1,0:21:25.22,0:21:26.30,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,可以啊  珊迪
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.22,0:21:26.30,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Sure thing, Sandy
Dialogue: 1,0:21:26.64,0:21:27.39,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,海绵宝宝
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.64,0:21:27.39,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,SpongeBob?
Dialogue: 1,0:21:27.39,0:21:27.93,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.39,0:21:27.93,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Yeah?
Dialogue: 1,0:21:27.93,0:21:28.68,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你觉得
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.93,0:21:28.68,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Do you think
Dialogue: 1,0:21:29.68,0:21:31.10,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你觉得我可以切这块吗
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.68,0:21:31.10,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Do you think I could cut this one?
Dialogue: 1,0:21:32.10,0:21:32.72,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,可以
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.10,0:21:32.72,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Sure
Dialogue: 1,0:21:32.72,0:21:33.35,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,谢谢了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.72,0:21:33.35,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Thanks
Dialogue: 1,0:21:36.27,0:21:37.31,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,切够了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.27,0:21:37.31,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Is that enough?
Dialogue: 1,0:21:37.81,0:21:39.23,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,再切一块吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.81,0:21:39.23,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Maybe just one more
Dialogue: 1,0:21:40.15,0:21:40.86,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,两块也行
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.15,0:21:40.86,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Or two
Dialogue: 1,0:21:40.86,0:21:41.65,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,三块也行
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.86,0:21:41.65,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Or three
Dialogue: 1,0:21:41.65,0:21:42.15,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,十块也行
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.65,0:21:42.15,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Or ten
Dialogue: 1,0:21:42.15,0:21:42.57,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,十块
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.15,0:21:42.57,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Ten
Dialogue: 1,0:21:42.57,0:21:43.24,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,好  就十块
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.57,0:21:43.24,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Yes, ten
Dialogue: 1,0:21:43.24,0:21:44.74,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,因为我们真的好饿
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.24,0:21:44.74,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Because we're really hungry
Dialogue: 1,0:21:44.95,0:21:46.61,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.95,0:21:46.61,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Right
Dialogue: 1,0:21:48.41,0:21:49.74,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,该放面包了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.41,0:21:49.74,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Time for buns
Dialogue: 1,0:21:51.79,0:21:53.16,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,来点番茄怎么样
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.79,0:21:53.16,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,How about some tomatoes?
Dialogue: 1,0:21:53.16,0:21:54.29,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我来切奶酪
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.16,0:21:54.29,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,And I'll cut the cheese
Dialogue: 1,0:21:58.21,0:21:59.21,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,还要再切什么
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.21,0:21:59.21,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,And, what else should we slice?
Dialogue: 1,0:21:59.46,0:22:00.09,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,再切面包
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.46,0:22:00.09,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,More buns
Dialogue: 1,0:22:00.09,0:22:00.79,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,还有生菜
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.09,0:22:00.79,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,And lettuce
Dialogue: 1,0:22:09.68,0:22:11.97,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,做三明治可真是好玩
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.68,0:22:11.97,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Making sandwiches sure is fun
Dialogue: 1,0:22:11.97,0:22:12.72,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,对吧  珊迪
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.97,0:22:12.72,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Right, Sandy
Dialogue: 1,0:22:13.31,0:22:13.81,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,对吧
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.31,0:22:13.81,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Right?
Dialogue: 1,0:22:14.52,0:22:16.02,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我看我现在要吃个三明治了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.52,0:22:16.02,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I guess I'll eat one now
Dialogue: 1,0:22:20.36,0:22:22.44,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你要被我剁碎了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.36,0:22:22.44,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You're mince meat
Dialogue: 1,0:22:22.44,0:22:24.03,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你做梦
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.44,0:22:24.03,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,In your dreams
Dialogue: 1,0:22:33.33,0:22:34.29,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,真是见鬼了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.33,0:22:34.29,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What the barnacle
Dialogue: 1,0:22:38.62,0:22:41.00,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你觉得蟹老板搞过空手道吗
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.62,0:22:41.00,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Do you think Mr. Krabs ever does karate?
Dialogue: 1,0:22:42.96,0:22:44.05,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,蟹老板
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.96,0:22:44.05,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Mr. Krabs
Dialogue: 1,0:22:45.51,0:22:47.22,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,蟹老板  近来可好
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.51,0:22:47.22,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Mr. Krabs, how's it going?
Dialogue: 1,0:22:47.72,0:22:48.80,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,今天很美好吧
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.72,0:22:48.80,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Nice day, huh?
Dialogue: 1,0:22:51.89,0:22:53.39,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,好吧  蟹老板
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.89,0:22:53.39,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Alright, Mr. Krabs
Dialogue: 1,0:22:53.39,0:22:54.35,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你抓了我个现行
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.39,0:22:54.35,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You caught me
Dialogue: 1,0:22:54.35,0:22:55.39,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,可你知道吗
Dialogue: 0,0:22:54.35,0:22:55.39,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,But you know what?
Dialogue: 1,0:22:55.39,0:22:57.23,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我就是忍不住
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.39,0:22:57.23,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I just can't help myself
Dialogue: 1,0:22:57.81,0:22:59.44,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你开除我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.81,0:22:59.44,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You're just gonna have to fire me
Dialogue: 1,0:22:59.44,0:23:00.90,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,开除你
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.44,0:23:00.90,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Fire ya?
Dialogue: 1,0:23:00.90,0:23:03.40,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我想到了别的办法
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.90,0:23:03.40,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I've got something else in mind
Dialogue: 0,0:23:04.07,0:23:06.23,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(345.493,414)}蟹堡王
Dialogue: 1,0:23:13.16,0:23:14.99,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我爱空手道
Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.16,0:23:14.99,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I love karate
Dialogue: 1,0:23:15.62,0:23:17.20,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我爱空手道
Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.62,0:23:17.20,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I love kara-tay
Dialogue: 1,0:23:17.20,0:23:19.16,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我爱赚钱道
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.20,0:23:19.16,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I love money-ay
Dialogue: 1,0:23:19.16,0:23:20.67,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我恨你们仨
Dialogue: 0,0:23:19.16,0:23:20.67,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I hate all of you
